cs_abscond_PRO - my remake on original cs_abscond (http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/12331) by kan3;  alot models & textures are taken from it.

Features of this map:
* high fps (faster then cs_office)
* good ballance & gameplay
* nice degsign as you can see in screenshots
 
Have a nice play, hope you like it! (and personnaly - hope kan3 like it ;) )
